-- B y   T a k u   K a t o
-- 2010-09-28T08:30:32Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-09-28/takefuji-files-for-bankruptcy-after-being-forced-to-pay-refunds-to-clients.html
Takefuji Corp., a Japanese consumer
lender, filed for bankruptcy protection today with the Tokyo
District Court, according a statement from the company to the
Tokyo Stock Exchange.     To contact the reporter on this story:
